headline: MetLife Xcelerator Hits 4.5 Million Active Consumers and Surpasses $200M in Premiums
summary: NEW YORK, March 19, 2025--MetLife, a global leader in insurance solutions, announces the creation of a new regional business unit in Latin America by the name of MetLife Xcelerator, marking a significant milestone in the evolution of the MetLife Xcelerator platform and execution of the company’s New Frontier strategy.
